rately represent the ionization dynamics, i.e.,\nthe discharge operation mode. This work represents also a successful\nexperimental validation of the discharge model developed for neon-oxygen CCPs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 May 2022 04:20:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
