 the\nsupernova decay and the cloud returns to an almost indistinguishable state from\nan un-shocked cloud, in spite of the global ambient pressure drop. In neither\nsupernova-cloud scenario do we see any local gravitational collapse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 May 2022 07:06:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-16"}
