(ii) directly model mechanisms of human reasoning, such as beliefs and bias,\nwithout going necessarily learning via trial-and-error.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 May 2022 07:33:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-16"}
